Package: envc
Title: Detect Electronic Nonverbal Cues in Text
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Saif", "Ahmed", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "saif@example.com"),
    person("Kokil", "Jaidka", role = "aut"))
Description: Detects electronic nonverbal cues (eNVCs) in text-based
    communication. Implements a taxonomy of kinesic and paralinguistic
    cues grounded in nonverbal communication theory, including emoji
    detection, capitalization, elongation, vocalics, and expressive
    punctuation. Based on Ahmed et al. (2026), ICWSM.
